          '¹All things in the Heavens and the Earth glorify Allah; the Almighty, the Wise.²The Heavens and the Earth are in His control; He gives life, death and has absolute control over all things.³He is the First and the Last, the Evident and the Unseen and the Knower of all things.⁴He created Heavens and the Earth in six days, then established Himself on His Throne (as befits Him). He knows what goes inside the Earth and what comes out from it, and what comes down from the sky, and what goes up. He is with you wherever you are, and sees whatever you do.⁵He has the control of the Heavens and the Earth and all things will return to Allah.⁶He extends the night into the day, and the day into the night, (so varying the length of day and night). He is the Knower of the secrets of the mind.',
